psalm.text:
[[Ps 138,1]]I will give thanks to you, O LORD, with all my heart, 
for you have heard the words of my mouth; 
in the presence of the angels I will sing your praise;
[[Ps 138,2a]]I will worship at your holy temple.

[[Ps 138,2b]]I will give thanks to your name,
[[Ps 138,2c]]because of your kindness and your truth.
[[Ps 138,3]]When I called, you answered me; 
you built up strength within me.

[[Ps 138,6]]The LORD is exalted, yet the lowly he sees, 
and the proud he knows from afar.
[[Ps 138,8]]The LORD will complete what he has done for me; 
your kindness, O LORD, endures forever; 
forsake not the work of your hands.
